verbose_text: Furthermore, the levels of Gapdh expression detected by quantitative RT-PCR were also within a narrow range for all groups (Ct Gapdh = 18.89 +/- 0.52 for Hoxc8-transgenic samples versus Ct Gapdh = 18.79 +/- 0.68 for controls, and Ct Gapdh = 18.39 +/- 0.69 for Hoxd4-transgenic samples versus Ct Gapdh = 18.29 +/- 0.66 for controls).
